{"tid":102208,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想學好calculus，有咩書推介？","createTime":"2017-01-31T12:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T17:01:21.000Z","uid":22604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d15a2559a35680c984e79324a05ee82e3e436c","tid":102208,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:48:19.000Z","msg":"中學淨係讀過m1，得少少式背睇落好易。<br />\n<br />\n而家讀上去啲嘢愈黎愈癲，就連啲basic嘢例如double integral 都唔識<br />\n<br />\n想由頭開始慢慢讀好differentiation 同 integration，想問吓巴打們有咩書推介，同埋上網搵佐兩本，可唔可以比較吓：<br />\nCalculus Made Easy by Thompson<br />\nCalsulus: A New Horizon, Combined, 6th Edition by Howard Anton<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80555085075fc5ea5e41d22883d29f53478d3ee8","tid":102208,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"留明學野"},{"pid":"d78a0b3eeecfd951bcc4596b8269f1282150762e","tid":102208,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"會唔會試下大學啲入門課程<br />\n啲notes 我覺得幾好"},{"pid":"837619f67b93fef5798715fd4a9345245564d9f1","tid":102208,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會試下大學啲入門課程<br />\n啲notes 我覺得幾好</blockquote><br />\n就係讀佐幾個course 都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時聽唔明就會上youtube 睇啲鬼佬tutorial<br />\n慢慢開始意識到咁樣讀好無系統，所以先想跟一本比較全面，有系統嘅書去慢慢學。"},{"pid":"8eb0fadff89bc3ef577aac4237cb691b6792ae2d","tid":102208,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec3d4a28059e4c6d8f4775fac1e8f42c38f008a","tid":102208,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Thomas Calculus</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講吓同<br />\nCalculus Made Easy by Thompson<br />\nCalculus: A New Horizon, Combined, 6th Edition by Howard Anton<br />\n呢兩本有咩分別<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"46ba0de0ada1673c62b34cd66b867dcd1ca2e04d","tid":102208,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"你依家calculus程度係點？<br />\n<br />\n你讀咩major<br />\n唔同major對calculus有唔同要求"},{"pid":"a1d0786a89fbba75b5a0b477535f5183b1a0ab3d","tid":102208,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你依家calculus程度係點？<br />\n<br />\n你讀咩major<br />\n唔同major對calculus有唔同要求</blockquote><br />\n如果無讀過<br />\n想入門 學d最基本既野<br />\n有無推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92868bcfb1133df7596fb2319b16c13590fdea58","tid":102208,"uid":40460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"舊制嘅a maths, pure maths 書都得卦？"},{"pid":"70a0b8a43ff84aad5cb0e15c9c4abeb82bc2fd9a","tid":102208,"uid":6462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"schaums outline,最快最清唔累墜"},{"pid":"537c139db0e496f7311e7ef3bec9c066b27ad428","tid":102208,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你依家calculus程度係點？<br />\n<br />\n你讀咩major<br />\n唔同major對calculus有唔同要求</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟讀statistics<br />\ncalculus仲係m1 背式嘅程度<br />\ndifferentiation 知道first principle, chain rule product rule quotient rule<br />\nintegration 就識得sub u= g(x) 同埋integration by part<br />\n我諗淨係咁多到<br />\n<br />\n跟住statistics 要讀好多continuous random variables 嘅distribution就開始唔掂"},{"pid":"fe4b5d59edcdb8549c8c9d0d6f3a2dca2823abeb","tid":102208,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"上youtube 睇片"},{"pid":"b006a3ba51d1e30d07e57f285d82d4885210cf21","tid":102208,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊制嘅a maths, pure maths 書都得卦？</blockquote><br />\n喺邊度可以搵到？<br />\n同埋始終都係備試參考書，會唔會解得唔夠全面<br />\n我想每一個根基都打好佢，如果都係解啲唔解啲咁我就會揀其他書"},{"pid":"f717795025d71d2fde3a7124277323eef9e7d6ad","tid":102208,"uid":40822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己睇到Vector個度唔係好明 !"},{"pid":"f45c46f31574fbac84b157340faaa27a5d9f9538","tid":102208,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Thomas Calculus</blockquote><br />\nThomas Calculus x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bc9d164a09cc70bea58bb200fddf0706df29b2","tid":102208,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"多數千幾頁有15~16課 由single variable functions到vector calculus嘅calculus書都差唔多<br />\n應該唔會有人講到俾你聽有咩唔同 因為唔會有人得閒到同樣嘢睇兩次"},{"pid":"7b85c65abc28945cb937984850f2a029b30f316f","tid":102208,"uid":23345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"我依家用緊 single variable calculus 3rd edition by James Stewart 幾好用不過要睇下你想學嘅程度喺邊度"},{"pid":"01cca87c2b83b9234b64fe4e0c48fc02d61a24d0","tid":102208,"uid":81222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"上YouTube 睇啦<br />\n因為啲19 textbk成日好多廢話<br />\n變相浪費好多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93262518a46e32025c68ee7f45533cdf685cc121","tid":102208,"uid":81099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"Rudin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇明呢本就得"},{"pid":"74ab274eca110a6eb74a7538c07e897231a53a12","tid":102208,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"冇讀過m1，不過大學take maths course 唔多唔少都會用到。如果你係m1個類最基本嘅 Calculus，可以考慮下Essential Calculus with Applications (Richard A. Silverman)同埋 Thomas calculus"},{"pid":"d05965eee8a190fd7d99f832b92b51404fdee3e2","tid":102208,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"多謝樓上咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋幫佐小弟好大忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8485bd09e709d77cc0dfa4700a78840f748d354","tid":102208,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"我岩岩睇左陣知乎<br />\n有人recommend coursera上面個 calculus one 唔洗錢的<br />\n2月20會開<br />\n如果想自己睇video就算 可以youtube 搵jim fowler 其實同一條友 不過可能佢依幾年改左課程你唔知<br />\n有埋本258 頁既online textbook 都係唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47dca461b414a50668879f7b00192927788ee14","tid":102208,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"Stewart寫得浅白過Thomas"},{"pid":"f3b8d56ece8c40357448dcb8909ccd7b1097ab83","tid":102208,"uid":59532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"youtube 搵Khan academy"},{"pid":"41b7e742bb716b03beb195a765b43a7245e6f961","tid":102208,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>youtube 搵Khan academy</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}